import React, { useState } from 'react'
import BottomNavigation from '@mui/material/BottomNavigation';
import BottomNavigationAction from '@mui/material/BottomNavigationAction';
import FolderIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Folder';
import RestoreIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Restore';
import FavoriteIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Favorite';
import LocationOnIcon from '@mui/icons-material/LocationOn';
import { Button, Divider, Grid, List, ListItem, ListItemButton, ListItemText, Paper, Typography } from '@mui/material';
import { Box } from '@mui/system';
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';


const HighlightSection = () => {


    return (
        <>
        <Divider>
            <Typography variant='h5'>
                Never Stop Learning
            </Typography>
        </Divider>

        <Grid container spacing={2} align="center" mt={2}>
            {/* CONTACT US */}
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={4} md={4} >
                <Box>
                    <FolderIcon />
                    <Typography variant='h5'>
                        Public Classes
                    </Typography>

                    <Typography variant='p' display="block">
                        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Fuga, cupiditate? Consectetur corrupti corporis dolore consequatur fuga fugit, doloremque repellendus quod.
                    </Typography>

                    <Button variant="outlined" mt={2}>
                        Outlined
                    </Button>
                </Box>
            </Grid>

            {/* NEVER STOP LEARNING */}
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={4} md={4}>
            <Box sx={{justifyContent: 'left', fontSize: '20px'}}>
                    <Typography variant='h5'>
                        Contact Us
                    </Typography>

                    <Typography variant='h5'>
                        Phone: ###.###.####
                    </Typography>

                    <Typography variant='h5'>
                        Email: ###.###.####
                    </Typography>

                    <FolderIcon /> < FolderIcon/> 
                </Box>
            </Grid>

            {/* COFFEE GEEK REPORTS */}
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={4} md={4}>
            <Box >
                    <Typography variant='h5'>
                        Contact Us
                    </Typography>

                    <Typography variant='h5'>
                        Phone: ###.###.####
                    </Typography>

                    <Typography variant='h5'>
                        Email: ###.###.####
                    </Typography>

                    <FolderIcon /> < FolderIcon/> 
                </Box>
            </Grid>
        </Grid>
        </>
      );
}

export default HighlightSection
